            "title": "Formatting Rules 📋",
            "content": "# Key PEP 8 Rules\n\n* **Indentation:** 4 spaces (not tabs)\n* **Line length:** Max 79 characters\n* **Blank lines:** 2 between functions\n* **Imports:** One per line, at top\n* **Spaces:** Around operators"
        },
