            "title": "Best Practices 🏆",
            "content": "# Write Better Code\n\n1. **DRY** — Don't Repeat Yourself\n2. **KISS** — Keep It Simple\n3. **Meaningful names** — Self-documenting\n4. **Small functions** — One job each\n5. **Comments** — Explain why, not what"
        },
